# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# combined — __aexit__, __await__, __anext__ across all 8 multiprocessing subjects
#
# Covers the full matrix: 8 classes x 3 methods = 24 rows.
# __aexit__:  all false — no async context manager support.
# __await__:  all false — multiprocessing.pool.AsyncResult is not asyncio-awaitable.
# __anext__:  all false — no async iteration support.
# All three async protocol methods are absent from all eight classes' own __dict__.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

